snippet.title: Renovation Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Recorded directly off of the original Evercade handheld. All of the games in the cart are Mega Drive / Genesis games and are expensive and rare, since all of these never saw a release in Europe.

Games:
00:00:08 - Arcus Odyssey
00:05:25 - Beast Wrestler
00:10:30 - Dino Land
00:19:03 - El Viento
00:24:49 - Exile
00:31:30 - Final Zone
00:36:12 - Gaiares
00:39:58 - Granada
00:42:51 - Sol-Deace
00:46:20 - Traysia
00:59:17 - Valis
01:09:17 - Valis III
